    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative, boasting a fully bulletproofed VANOS system utilizing Beisan components and documented rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with surgical precision, sending power through a refreshed limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with a structural foam and plate kit, ensuring total rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension features upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers for optimized geometry. Finished in a pristine, original paint with zero oxidation, this is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
