      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows no signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free of any swirls, stone chips, or door dings, and has been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats are supple without any creases, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that fresh, new-car scent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively performed by certified technicians using OEM parts. It drives with the same precision and smoothness as the day it was first delivered. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-grade example of this model.",
      "price": 44800.0,
